        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【报价】Porsche Design Honor Magic V2 RSR 国行抵港速试　手感超佳 + 机身超有型</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/honor-magic-v2-rsr-porsche-design-china-ver-in-hk/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=honor-magic-v2-rsr-porsche-design-china-ver-in-hk</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/honor-magic-v2-rsr-porsche-design-china-ver-in-hk/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 13:20:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[honor]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Magic V2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[porsche design]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RSR]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221599</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>之前我们都为大家提及过，Huawei 已宣布正式与 Porsche Design 结束合作关系，而后者现在就改为与 Honor 合作，而最近他们推出的 Porsche Design Honor Magic V2 RSR 国行「大折」就迅速引入香港市场，究竟这部称为「波子」牌头首部折机初步玩起来手感如何？就让 Edward 带大家去看看，并同时为大家报导它的定价吧。</p><h2>超型格外形 + 钛合金手感铰位</h2><p>今次 Honor 与 Porsche Design 合作推出的这部 Magic V2 RSR（下文简称 V2 RSR），基本来说机身布局与一般版的 Magic V2 是几乎相同的，不过 V2 RSR 的机背虽然仍是采用玻璃物料，但所采用的 Agate Grey 深灰色配色加上磨砂工艺后无论看还是摸上去也很有金属感。此外，它的机背中央亦加入了微微拱起的线条，类似模拟 Porsche 车身的 Flyline 设计，令这部特别版「大折」很有 Porsche 名跑的感觉。至于铰位方面，虽然仍然采用金属物料制造，但外表的磨砂令它很像钛合金物料的手感，配合机背设计，摸上手对手感有很大提升。此外，它的相机模组亦比一般版更加大亦更加有型，整体看起来设计很有心思。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221602" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155813-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155813-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155813.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V2 RSR 的机背虽然仍是用上强化玻璃物料，但就加入磨砂工艺，所以无论看起来还是摸上手，金属感亦十分明显，另外，磨砂设计亦令机背不易留下指纹，使用体验更佳。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221603" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155818-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155818-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155818.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机背中央凸起了一条线，模拟 Porsche 超跑流线型车身的设计，型格十足。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155828-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155828-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155828.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而 V2 RSR 的相机模组不但变大了很多，也是模仿 Porsche 跑车的溜背舷窗，令手机设计极具超跑感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160445-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160445-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160445.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于机身铰位用料上，V2 RSR（上）与一般版 Magic V2（下）也有不同，看起来十分相似，但摸上手 V2 RSR 的铰位外壳更像时下流行的钛合金物料。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155953-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155953-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155953.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲加上 V2 RSR 仍然保留了一般版 Magic V2 的轻薄设计，所以作为 Porsche Design 推出的第一部折机，V2 RSR 真的做得十分出色，上手使用手感亦是上佳。</p><h2>包装附送机套触控笔</h2><p>此外，Honor V2 RSR 的包装亦十分有心思，不但附送超美的真皮手机背盖，亦附送一般版没有的 Honor 触控笔，就连笔亦设有独立外携盒方便大家带出街使用。而作为超跑特别版的「大折」，V2 RSR 亦有附送车充，而车充与手机本身的充电器也同样支援 66W 有线快充，这个配套及设计也可见出厂商超有心思。至于硬件方面，大致上与 Magic V2 一般版差不多，同样是内建了 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 处理器、16GB RAM、6.43 吋 2376 x 1060 解像度 120Hz 更新率外荧幕、7.92 吋 2344 x 2156 解像度 120Hz 更新率可折式内荧幕、3 镜式主相机（5,000 万像素主摄 + 5,000 万像素超广角 + 2,000 万像素远摄）及 5,000mAh 容量电池，不过 V2 RSR 就有提供 1TB 容量的内存，对用家来说应该十分够用了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155400-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155400-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155400.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V2 RSR 随机是附送 Honor 自家的触控笔，与一般版十分不同（一般版是需要另购的）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155714-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155714-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155714.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不只送笔，随机亦附送触控笔的外携盒，十分细心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155705-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155705-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155705.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而且无论是手机背及铰位保护盖，还是触控笔外携盒，也是采用真皮物料制造，设计十分用心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155442-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155442-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155442.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155525-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155525-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155525.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Honor 另一个细心之处，就是附送的充电火牛除了有一般的 66W 快充火牛外，还为有车一族附送同样支援 66W 有线快充的车充。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221612" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155950-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155950-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155950.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221613" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160005-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160005-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V2 RSR 的外荧幕及内荧幕，与一般版相同，同样分别是 6.43 吋及 7.92 吋。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221614" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160321-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160321-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160321.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲荧幕依然支援 120Hz 更新率，显示效果仍然十分理想。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221615" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160058-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160058-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160058.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不过介面上某程预载程式就换上了 Porsche Design 风格的图示，令机身内外设计归于统一。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160042-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160042-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_160042.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲硬件配置大致与一般版 Magic V2 相同，不过它的内存就增大至 1TB，对用家来说应该十分够用。</p><p>至于定价方面，香港店舖开价为 $18,800，其实也只是比国内开价贵了千多元而已，而且以这部奢华超跑「大折」来说，开价亦算合理。对「波子」版手机有爱的用家，不妨考虑一下？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221617" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155322-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155322-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240223_155322-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>售价：$18,800</strong><br /><strong>查询：三禾电气（6838 1001）</strong><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/01/honor-v-purse-china-version-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】HONOR V Purse 国行　外形　手感　折叠功能　荧幕　相机　效能开箱评测</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/25/huawei-porsche-design-partnership/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为与 Porsche Design 合作告终　改与荣耀品牌合作</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/12/honor-magic-v2-announce-in-hk/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【报价】Honor 2 代折机 Magic V2 港行正式推出　定价进取 + 预订礼品吸引</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/honor-magic-v2-rsr-porsche-design-china-ver-in-hk/mobile-phone/">【报价】Porsche Design Honor Magic V2 RSR 国行抵港速试　手感超佳 + 机身超有型</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
