            <title>BYD 纯电超跑「仰望 U9」卖 186 万元    1300 匹马力破百 2.36 秒</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/byd-u9/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=byd-u9</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/byd-u9/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 12:30:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[byd]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[仰望 U9]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221530</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>据中国媒体报道，BYD 旗下品牌仰望正式推出仰望 U9 超跑，新车售价为人民币 168 万元（约港币 186 万元），0-100 公里加速时间为 2.36 秒，极速可达每小时 309 公里。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/r4cars4-694x361.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="361" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/r4cars4-694x361.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/r4cars4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>据中国媒体《汽车之家》报道，仰望 U9 使用「易四方」及「云辇-X」技术。「易四方」技术使 U9 的四个车轮可以独立驱动，至于「云辇-X」技术则是智能车身控制系统，据报 U9 可以原地弹跳和跳舞。购买仰望 U9 新车原厂会附送「整车包修」、8 年免费保养及 10 年免费 5G 车联网流量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221536" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/408432940_1708865415-694x395.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="395" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/408432940_1708865415-694x395.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/408432940_1708865415.jpg 1231w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>设计方面，官方表示采用了「时空之门」为主要设计语言。据中国媒体报道，主要可在车头大灯看见这种设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221537" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：汽车之家</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221538" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲车头部分可以看见不少为改良空气动力而加入的导流片、风口等<br />
图片来源：汽车之家</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-2-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-2-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-2.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲车身侧面呈现「低趴俯冲」式设计<br />
图片来源：汽车之家</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-3-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-3-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1400x0_1_q95_autohom-3.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲车尾设有大尺寸电动扰流版<br />
